trans-unit.source: Note: Font rotations can cause text baselines to be rotated, and multiple runs with different rotations can cause the baseline to bend or zig-zag. In order to account for this (rare) possibility, some APIs are specified to return metrics and take parameters 'in baseline-relative coordinates' (e.g. ascent, advance), and others are in 'in standard coordinates' (e.g. getBounds). Values in baseline-relative coordinates map the 'x' coordinate to the distance along the baseline, (positive x is forward along the baseline), and the 'y' coordinate to a distance along the perpendicular to the baseline at 'x' (positive y is 90 degrees clockwise from the baseline vector). Values in standard coordinates are measured along the x and y axes, with 0,0 at the origin of the TextLayout. Documentation for each relevant API indicates what values are in what coordinate system. In general, measurement-related APIs are in baseline-relative coordinates, while display-related APIs are in standard coordinates.

trans-unit.source: Notification is provided as two separate events, DocumentEvent, and UndoableEditEvent. If an undoable edit is undone, a DocumentEvent should be fired from the Document to indicate it has changed again. trans-unit.source: Notification type denoting that the memory usage of a memory pool has reached or exceeded its usage threshold value.
trans-unit.target: 表示内存池的内存使用量已达到或超过其使用量阈值的通知类型。

trans-unit.source: Notification type denoting that the memory usage of a memory pool has reached or exceeded its usage threshold value. This notification is emitted by MemoryMXBean. Subsequent crossing of the usage threshold value does not cause further notification until the memory usage has returned to become less than the usage threshold value. The value of this notification type is java.management.memory.threshold.exceeded.
trans-unit.target: 表示内存池的内存使用量已达到或超过其使用量阈值的通知类型。该通知由 MemoryMXBean 发出。直到内存使用量返回到小于使用量阈值为止，使用量阈值的后续跨越不会引起进一步的通知。此通知类型的值为 java.management.memory.threshold.exceeded 。

trans-unit.source: Notification type denoting that the memory usage of a memory pool is greater than or equal to its collection usage threshold after the Java virtual machine has expended effort in recycling unused objects in that memory pool.
trans-unit.target: 通知类型，表示在Java虚拟机已花费大量精力回收该内存池中的未使用对象之后，该内存池的内存使用量大于或等于其收集使用量阈值。

trans-unit.source: Notification type denoting that the memory usage of a memory pool is greater than or equal to its collection usage threshold after the Java virtual machine has expended effort in recycling unused objects in that memory pool. This notification is emitted by MemoryMXBean. The value of this notification type is java.management.memory.collection.threshold.exceeded.
trans-unit.target: 通知类型，表示在Java虚拟机已花费大量精力回收该内存池中的未使用对象之后，该内存池的内存使用量大于或等于其收集使用量阈值。该通知由 MemoryMXBean 发出。此通知类型的值为 java.management.memory.collection.threshold.exceeded 。

trans-unit.source: Notifications can be received by a listener, which is an object that implements the NotificationListener interface. You can add a listener to an MBean with the method MBeanServer.addNotificationListener(ObjectName, NotificationListener, NotificationFilter, Object). You can optionally supply a filter to this method, to select only notifications of interest. A filter is an object that implements the NotificationFilter interface.
trans-unit.target: 侦听器可以接收通知，侦听器是实现 NotificationListener 接口的对象。您可以使用 MBeanServer.addNotificationListener(ObjectName, NotificationListener, NotificationFilter, Object) 方法将侦听器添加到MBean 。您可以选择为此方法提供过滤器，以仅选择感兴趣的通知。过滤器是实现 NotificationFilter 接口的对象。

trans-unit.source: Notifications can be received by a listener, which is an object that implements the NotificationListener interface. You can add a listener to an MBean with the method MBeanServer.addNotificationListener(ObjectName, NotificationListener, NotificationFilter, Object). You can optionally supply a filter to this method, to select only notifications of interest. A filter is an object that implements the NotificationFilter interface.
trans-unit.target: 侦听器可以接收通知，侦听器是实现 NotificationListener 接口的对象。您可以使用 MBeanServer.addNotificationListener(ObjectName, NotificationListener, NotificationFilter, Object) 方法将侦听器添加到MBean 。您可以选择为此方法提供过滤器，以仅选择感兴趣的通知。过滤器是实现 NotificationFilter 接口的对象。

trans-unit.source: Notifies ListSelectionListeners added directly to the list of selection changes made to the selection model.
trans-unit.target: 通知 ListSelectionListener ,它直接添加到对选择模型所做的选择更改列表中。

trans-unit.source: Notifies ListSelectionListeners added directly to the list of selection changes made to the selection model. JList listens for changes made to the selection in the selection model, and forwards notification to listeners added to the list directly, by calling this method.
trans-unit.target: 通知 ListSelectionListener ,它直接添加到对选择模型所做的选择更改列表中。 JList 侦听在选择模型中对选择所做的更改，并通过调用此方法将通知转发给直接添加到列表的侦听器。

trans-unit.source: Notifies ListSelectionListeners that the value of the selection, in the closed interval firstIndex, lastIndex, has changed.
trans-unit.target: 通知 ListSelectionListeners 在封闭时间间隔 firstIndex ， lastIndex 中的选择值已更改。

trans-unit.source: Notifies PopupMenuListeners that the popup portion of the combo box has become invisible.
trans-unit.target: 通知 PopupMenuListener ，组合框的弹出部分已变得不可见。

trans-unit.target: 通知 PopupMenuListener ，组合框的弹出部分已被取消。

trans-unit.source: Notifies PopupMenuListeners that the popup portion of the combo box will become visible.
trans-unit.target: 通知 PopupMenuListener ，组合框的弹出部分将变为可见。

trans-unit.target: 通知 PopupMenuListener ，该弹出菜单将变为不可见。

trans-unit.source: Notifies PopupMenuListeners that this popup menu will become visible.
trans-unit.target: 通知 PopupMenuListener ，此弹出菜单将变为可见。

trans-unit.source: Notifies PopupMenuListeners that this popup menu is cancelled.
trans-unit.target: 通知 PopupMenuListeners 此弹出菜单已取消。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all ChangeListeners when the views size, position, or the viewports extent size has changed.
trans-unit.target: 当视图大小，位置或视口范围大小更改时，通知所有 ChangeListeners 。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that all cell values in the table's rows may have changed.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有的监听者,表中的所有单元格值可能已经改变。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that all cell values in the table's rows may have changed. The number of rows may also have changed and the JTable should redraw the table from scratch. The structure of the table (as in the order of the columns) is assumed to be the same.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有侦听器表行中的所有单元格值可能已更改。行数也可能已更改，并且 JTable 应该从头开始重绘该表。假定表的结构（按列的顺序）是相同的。

trans-unit.target: 通知所有在此对象上注册树选择事件的监听器。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的听众。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is created lazily.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的监听者。事件实例会被懒惰地创建。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created using the command parameter.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对此事件类型有通知兴趣的侦听器。事件实例是使用 command 参数延迟创建的。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created using the event parameter.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对此事件类型有通知兴趣的侦听器。事件实例是使用 event 参数延迟创建的。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created using the path parameter.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对此事件类型有通知兴趣的侦听器。事件实例是使用 path 参数延迟创建的。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created using the parameters passed into the fire method.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的监听者。事件实例使用传递到fire方法的参数懒惰地创建。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created using the parameters passed into the fire method. The listener list is processed in a last-to-first manner.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的监听者。事件实例使用传递到fire方法的参数懒惰地创建。列表以最后一个到第一个的方式处理。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created using the parameters passed into the fire method. The listener list is processed last to first.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的监听者。事件实例使用传递到fire方法的参数懒惰地创建。监听者列表从最后一个到第一个进行处理。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的监听者。事件实例被懒惰地创建。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. The event instance is lazily created. The listener list is processed in last to first order.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对该事件类型的通知感兴趣的监听者。事件实例被懒惰地创建。列表按从最后一个到第一个的顺序处理。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that have registered interest for notification on this event type. This is normally called by the currently installed EditorKit if a content type that supports hyperlinks is currently active and there was activity with a link. The listener list is processed last to first.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有对此事件类型有通知兴趣的侦听器。如果支持超链接的内容类型当前处于活动状态，并且具有链接的活动，则通常由当前安装的 EditorKit 调用此方法。侦听器列表的处理是从后到前。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that rows in the range [firstRow, lastRow], inclusive, have been deleted.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有侦听器 [firstRow, lastRow] 范围内的行已被删除。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that rows in the range [firstRow, lastRow], inclusive, have been inserted.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有侦听器已插入 [firstRow, lastRow] 范围内的行。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that rows in the range [firstRow, lastRow], inclusive, have been updated.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有侦听器 [firstRow, lastRow] （包括）范围内的行已更新。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that the table's structure has changed.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有监听者,表的结构已经改变。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that the table's structure has changed. The number of columns in the table, and the names and types of the new columns may be different from the previous state. If the JTable receives this event and its autoCreateColumnsFromModel flag is set it discards any table columns that it had and reallocates default columns in the order they appear in the model. This is the same as calling setModel(TableModel) on the JTable.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有侦听器表的结构已更改。表中的列数以及新列的名称和类型可能与以前的状态不同。如果 JTable 接收到此事件，并且设置了它的 autoCreateColumnsFromModel 标志，它将丢弃它拥有的所有表列，并按照它们在模型中出现的顺序重新分配默认列。这与在 JTable 上调用 setModel(TableModel) 相同。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all listeners that the value of the cell at [row, column] has been updated.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有侦听器 [row, column] 处的单元格值已更新。

trans-unit.source: Notifies all of the listeners registered with this RowSet object that its entire contents have changed.
trans-unit.target: 通知所有向此 RowSet 对象注册的侦听器，其全部内容已更改。

trans-unit.target: 通知所有向此 RowSet 对象注册的侦听器，其行之一已更改。

trans-unit.source: Notifies any listeners if the model changes.
trans-unit.target: 如果模型发生变化,则通知任何监听者。

trans-unit.source: Notifies listener that the mapping has changed.
trans-unit.target: 通知监听者映射已经改变。

trans-unit.source: Notifies listener that the sort order has changed.
trans-unit.target: 通知监听者排序顺序已经改变。

trans-unit.source: Notifies listeners of a change in path. changePaths should contain instances of PathPlaceHolder.
trans-unit.target: changePaths应该包含PathPlaceHolder的实例。

trans-unit.target: 通知监听者一个属性变化。

trans-unit.target: 通知听众,我们已经结束了一系列的调整。

trans-unit.target: 通知注册的侦听器 RowSet 对象的其中一行发生了更改。

trans-unit.source: Notifies registered listeners that a RowSet object in the given RowSetEvent object has changed its entire contents.
trans-unit.target: 通知注册的侦听器给定 RowSetEvent 对象中的 RowSet 对象已更改其全部内容。

trans-unit.source: Notifies registered listeners that a RowSet object's cursor has moved.
trans-unit.target: 通知注册的侦听器 RowSet 对象的光标已移动。

trans-unit.target: 通知注册的监听器,给定的RowSetEvent对象中的RowSet对象已经填充了一些额外的行。

trans-unit.source: Notifies registered listeners that a RowSet object in the given RowSetEvent object has populated a number of additional rows. The numRows parameter ensures that this event will only be fired every numRow.
trans-unit.target: 通知注册的侦听器给定RowSetEvent对象中的RowSet对象已填充了许多其他行。该 numRows 行参数确保该事件只会被激发每 numRow 行。

trans-unit.source: Notifies the LayerUI when any of its property are changed and enables updating every JLayer this LayerUI instance is set to.
trans-unit.target: 更改其任何属性时通知 LayerUI ，并允许更新此 LayerUI 实例设置为的每个 JLayer 。

trans-unit.source: Notifies the external quit requester that the quit will proceed, and performs the default QuitStrategy.
trans-unit.target: 通知外部退出请求者退出将继续，并执行默认的 QuitStrategy 。

trans-unit.source: Notifies the external quit requester that the user has explicitly canceled the pending quit, and leaves the application running.

trans-unit.source: Numbers in scientific notation are expressed as the product of a mantissa and a power of ten, for example, 1234 can be expressed as 1.234 x 10^3. The mantissa is often in the range 1.0 ≤ x < 10.0, but it need not be. DecimalFormat can be instructed to format and parse scientific notation only via a pattern; there is currently no factory method that creates a scientific notation format. trans-unit.source: Object that allows access to the static members of a class (its static methods, properties, and fields), as well as construction of instances using StandardOperation.NEW operation. In Dynalink, Class objects are not treated specially and act as ordinary Java objects; you can use e.g. GET:PROPERTY:superclass as a property getter to invoke clazz.getSuperclass(). On the other hand, you can not use Class objects to access static members of a class, nor to create new instances of the class using NEW. This is consistent with how Class objects behave in Java: in Java, you write e.g. new BitSet() instead of new BitSet.class(). Similarly, you write System.out and not System.class.out. It is this aspect of using a class name as the constructor and a namespace for static members that StaticClass embodies.
